curricula you learn a ton and

00:16:21.210 --> 00:16:26.390
ton of application, maybe
comprehension, Maxwell's

00:16:26.390 --> 00:16:29.290
equations, differentiation,
integration.

00:16:29.290 --> 00:16:30.940
Then we start to synthesize
stuff.

00:16:30.940 --> 00:16:32.760
You know, in your senior
year you do

00:16:32.760 --> 00:16:34.920
