00:32:55.300 --> 00:33:00.540
So the question is if you could
time travel back and

00:33:00.540 --> 00:33:04.120
talk to your earlier self what
one or two sentences would you

00:33:04.120 --> 00:33:06.370
tell your earlier self before
they started solving the

00:33:06.370 --> 00:33:08.930
problem that would make
the problem just

00:33:08.930 --> 00:33:10.600
sort of flow smoothly?

00:33:10.600 --> 00:33:11.850
OK?

00:33:30.610 --> 00:33:33.180
So what sentence would you tell
your earlier, pre-problem

00:33:33.180 --> 00:33:34.160
solved self?

00:33:34.160 --> 00:33:35.910
So this is after you
solved the problem.

00:33:41.620 --> 00:33:47.340
So that forces you to give a
insightful summary of what you

00:33:47.340 --> 00:33:48.720
learned from the problem.

00:33:48.720 --> 00:33:51.370
So it forces you towards the
intuitive way of reasoning.

00:33:51.370 --> 00:33:52.880
And you'll find it's quite
hard at first.

00:33:52.880 --> 00:33:54.550
Because you don't have the
intuitive library.

00:33:54.550 --> 00:33:56.990
