the joke.

00:38:08.040 --> 00:38:09.430
The problem was that
the joke wasn't

00:38:09.430 --> 00:38:12.280
related to the material.

00:38:12.280 --> 00:38:13.830
So the thing should
be interesting.

00:38:13.830 --> 00:38:14.970
Because you want to
draw people in.

00:38:14.970 --> 00:38:16.570
You don't want to conclude from
that article that you

00:38:16.570 --> 00:38:18.200
shouldn't start with
some interesting.

00:38:18.200 --> 00:38:19.570
