own in German.

00:39:57.000 --> 00:40:02.790
So somehow this vector belongs
to the matrix.

00:40:02.790 --> 00:40:04.450
It's said to be an eigenvector
of the matrix.

00:40:04.450 --> 00:40:08.340
It's preserved when you hit
it with the matrix.

00:40:08.340 --> 00:40:09.620
You get back the thing itself.

00:40:09.620 --> 00:40:11.975
And in that way it belongs
to the matrix.

00:40:11.975 --> 00:40:16.150
