01:09:12.560 --> 01:09:15.340
But I find that the response
rate has been dropping.

01:09:15.340 --> 01:09:16.819
What do you do about that?

01:09:16.819 --> 01:09:19.840
And I have to say, that I
found the same thing.

01:09:19.840 --> 01:09:21.550
This year I found
the same thing.

01:09:21.550 --> 01:09:24.779
Not in this class but in my
other class, whereas I didn't

01:09:24.779 --> 01:09:25.630
