and the American just because

01:35:30.290 --> 01:35:32.220
there's so many other social
variables that are so

01:35:32.220 --> 01:35:36.760
different like the population
that goes to university, which

01:35:36.760 --> 01:35:40.200
universities are talking about
the exam system itself, so I

01:35:40.200 --> 01:35:43.440
don't know of any studies that
have been done across cultures

01:35:43.440 --> 01:35:44.900
and that I would trust.

01:35:44.900 --> 01:35:47.310
And within I don't
know of any.

01:35:47.310 --> 01:35:49.570
But it's a good question.

01:35:49.570 --> 01:35:53.490
I know studies in general about
rewards, which is that

01:35:53.490 --> 01:35:58.480
the more you reward people for
things that they like the less

01:35:58.480 --> 01:36:00.570
they like doing them.

01:36:00.570 --> 01:36:03.510
So I might give you some
